    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a functional daily driver at a reasonable price. While the engine and transmission are operational and the car drives fine, there are noticeable signs of wear, including some minor exterior scratches and a cabin that shows its age. It has been maintained regularly, though it may soon require routine attention to some suspension components and minor fluid leaks. This is an honest, middle-of-the-road vehicle that offers good utility without the premium price of a newer model.",
